QuestData.Title: Shallow End of the Gene Pool
QuestData.Description: <Gurboggle inspects the Gnaws Tooth Necklace for a moment.>$b$bNot bad, $r, assuming it's the real thing. I'll hafta send one of my boys out to make sure your story checks out.$b$bIn the meantime, you're gunna do a little somethin' for me, see, 'cause this little trinket ain't worth givin' up The Pewter Pounder - not by a longshot!$b$bMy cousin, Gilblingle, has had his eye on my throne for years. Dumb as a bag of coral, that one - but still dangerous.$b$bYou take him out, and then we'll talk.
QuestData.LogDescription: King Gurboggle wants you to kill Gilblingle in Gurboggle's Ledge.
